---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import "@/styles/global.css"
---

<Layout>
    <main class="flex flex-col items-center py-10">
        <img src="/404.png" width="300" alt="404"/>
        <h1 class="text-3xl text-center font-bold">404: Not Found</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-500 text-center mt-5">
            요청하신 경로 
            <code>
                {typeof Astro.request.url === "string"
                  ? Astro.request.url : ""}
            </code>는<br/>
            저희 서버에 존재하지 않는 것 같아요!
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>